'''人馬座A*'''（Sagittarius A*，簡寫為'''Sgr A*'''，[[*|星號*]]讀作「star」或「星」<ref>{{Cite web |title=Astronomers reveal first image of the black hole at the heart of our galaxy |url=https://eventhorizontelescope.org/blog/astronomers-reveal-first-image-black-hole-heart-our-galaxy |access-date=May 12, 2022 |website=Event Horizon Telescope |language=en}}</ref>）是個位於[[銀河系|銀河系]][[銀心|中心]]的[[超大質量黑洞|超大質量黑洞]]<ref>{{Cite news |last=Parsons |first=Jeff |date=October 31, 2018 |title=Scientists find proof a supermassive black hole is lurking at the centre of the Milky Way |language=en-GB |work=Metro |url=https://metro.co.uk/2018/10/31/scientists-find-proof-a-supermassive-black-hole-is-lurking-at-the-centre-of-the-milky-way-8092994/ |url-status=live |access-date=October 31, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031214911/https://metro.co.uk/2018/10/31/scientists-find-proof-a-supermassive-black-hole-is-lurking-at-the-centre-of-the-milky-way-8092994/ |archive-date=October 31, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Mosher |first=Dave |last2=Business Insider |date=October 31, 2018 |title=A 'mind-boggling' telescope observation has revealed the point of no return for our galaxy's monster black hole |work=The Middletown Press |url=https://www.middletownpress.com/technology/businessinsider/article/Supermassive-black-holes-gorge-themselves-on-a-7971243.php |url-status=dead |access-date=May 16, 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031144008/https://www.middletownpress.com/technology/businessinsider/article/Supermassive-black-holes-gorge-themselves-on-a-7971243.php |archive-date=October 31, 2018}}</ref><ref name="plait">{{cite web |last1=Plait |first1=Phil |author-link=Phil Plait |date=November 7, 2018 |title=Astronomers See Material Orbiting a Black Hole *Right* at the Edge of Forever |url=https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/astronomers-see-material-orbiting-a-black-hole-right-at-the-edge-of-forever |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181110143143/https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/astronomers-see-material-orbiting-a-black-hole-right-at-the-edge-of-forever |archive-date=10 November 2018 |access-date=November 12, 2018 |website=Bad Astronomy |publisher=Syfy Wire |language=en}}</ref>。它位於星座[[人馬座|人馬座]]和[[天蠍座|天蠍座]]的邊界附近，大約位於[[黃道|黃道]]以南5.6°<ref>Calculated using [https://frostydrew.org/utilities.dc/convert/tool-eq_coordinates/pss-fdo/ Equatorial and Ecliptic Coordinates] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721134008/https://frostydrew.org/utilities.dc/convert/tool-eq_coordinates/pss-fdo/|date=July 21, 2019|title=}} calculator</ref>，視覺上接近[[蝴蝶星團|蝴蝶星團]]（M6）和[[尾宿八|尾宿八]]（天蠍座λ）。

這顆天體是明亮緻密的[[射電源|電波源]]。人馬座A*的名字有其歷史淵源。在 1954年<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Kraus |first1=J. D. |last2=Ko |first2=H. C. |last3=Matt |first3=S. |date=December 1954 |title=Galactic and localized source observations at 250 megacycles per second. |url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1954AJ.....59..439K |journal=[[The_Astronomical_Journal|The Astronomical Journal]] |volume=59 |pages=439–443 |bibcode=1954AJ.....59..439K |doi=10.1086/107059 |issn=0004-6256 |via=The ADS}}</ref>，[[約翰·丹尼爾·克勞斯|約翰·丹尼爾·克勞斯]]、柯賢清（Hsien-Ching Ko）和肖恩·馬特（Sean Matt）列出了他們用[[俄亥俄州立大學|俄亥俄州立大學]]電波望遠鏡在250MHz下確定的電波源。這些電波源按星座排列，並隨意的分配字母來標示，但字母A通常表示星座內最亮的電波源。[[星號|星號]] ''*'' 是因為它的發現被認為是"令人興奮的"<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Goss |first1=W. M. |last2=Brown |first2=Robert L. |last3=Lo |first3=K. Y. |date=August 8, 2003 |title=The Discovery of Sgr A* |url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/asna.200385047 |journal=Astronomische Nachrichten |language=en |volume=324 |issue=S1 |pages=497–504 |arxiv=astro-ph/0305074 |bibcode=2003ANS...324..497G |doi=10.1002/asna.200385047 |issn=0004-6337}}</ref>。這與用星號表示[[激發態|激發態]]原子的命名法一致（例如，[[氦|氦]]的激發態為He*）。星號是羅伯特·L·布朗於1982年設置<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Brown |first1=Robert L. |date=November 1, 1982 |title=Precessing Jets in Sagittarius A: Gas Dynamics in the Central Parsec of the Galaxy |url=https://adsabs.harvard.edu/full/1982ApJ...262..110B |journal=The Astrophysical Journal |volume=262 |pages=110–119 |bibcode=1982ApJ...262..110B |doi=10.1086/160401 |access-date=May 13, 2022}}</ref>，他知道，銀河系中心最强的電波發射似乎是源自於一個緊湊的非熱射電體。

它是非常光亮及緻密的[[無線電波源|無線電波源]]，大約每11分鐘[[自轉週期|自轉]]一圈<ref>[http://www.space.com/2089-tourist-guide-milky.html The New Tourist's Guide to the Milky Way | Space.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.space.com/2089-tourist-guide-milky.html |date=20210125011643 }} Sgr A* is also probably rotating, making one full revolution about every 11 minutes.</ref>。人馬座A*是目前人類觀測到离地球最近，被认为是研究[[黑洞|黑洞物理]]的最佳目标<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Melia |first=Fulvio |last2=Falcke |first2=Heino |date=2001-09 |title=The Supermassive Black Hole at the Galactic Center |url=https://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev.astro.39.1.309 |journal=Annual Review of Astronomy and Astrophysics |language=en |volume=39 |issue=1 |doi=10.1146/annurev.astro.39.1.309 |issn=0066-4146 |access-date=2022-05-15 |archive-date=2022-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220515083832/https://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev.astro.39.1.309 }}</ref>。

對圍繞人馬座A*運行的幾顆恆星的觀測，特別是[[S2_(恒星)|S2]]，已被用來確定物體的質量和半徑上限。基於質量和日益精確的半徑值，天文學家得出結論：人馬座A*一定是銀河系中央的超大質量黑洞<ref name="Henderson">{{cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/uk/science/article5316001.ece|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216235509/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/uk/science/article5316001.ece|archive-date=2008-12-16|title=Astronomers confirm black hole at the heart of the Milky Way|last=Henderson|first=Mark|date=2009-12-09 |publisher= Times Online|access-date=2019-06-06}}</ref>。其質量的當前值為4.154{{±|0.014}}百萬[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]。 <ref name="GRAVITY"/>。

[[赖因哈德·根策尔|赖因哈德·根策尔]](Reinhard Genzel)和[[安德烈娅·盖兹|安德烈娅·盖兹]](Andrea Ghez)因發現人馬座A*是一個超大質量緻密天體而獲得2020年[[諾貝爾物理學獎|諾貝爾物理學獎]]，而[[黑洞|黑洞]]是當時唯一合理的解釋<ref>{{cite news|date=6 October 2020|title=The Nobel Prize in Physics 2020|language=en-us|url=https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/physics/2020/summary/|access-date=7 October 2020|archive-date=24 April 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424115309/https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/physics/2020/summary/|url-status=live}}</ref>。

2022年5月12日，天文學家發佈於2017年4月使用全球射電天文臺網絡[[事件視界望遠鏡|事件視界望遠鏡]]製作的人馬座A*視界周圍[[吸積盤|吸積盤]]的第一張影像<ref name="AJ-202205">{{cite journal |last=Bower |first=Geoffrey C. |date=May 2022 |title=Focus on First Sgr A* Results from the Event Horizon Telescope |url=https://iopscience.iop.org/journal/2041-8205/page/Focus_on_First_Sgr_A_Results |journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]] |access-date=May 12, 2022}}</ref>，確認物體是黑洞。這是繼2019年[[M87|M87]]的[[室女座A星系#核心黑洞|超大質量黑洞]]之後，確認的第二張黑洞影像。<ref name="ESO2208">{{cite news|url=https://www.eso.org/public/news/eso2208-eht-mw/|title=Astronomers reveal first image of the black hole at the heart of our galaxy|work=eso.org|date=12 May 2022|access-date=12 May 2022}}</ref><ref name="NYT-20220512"/>。

== 觀察和描述 ==
[[File:X-RayFlare-BlackHole-MilkyWay-20140105.jpg|thumb]]閃焰<ref name="NASA-20150105"/>。]]

2022年5月12日，第一張人馬座A*的照片由[[事件視界望遠鏡|事件視界望遠鏡]]的合作單位共同發佈。這張影像基於2017年拍攝的無線電干涉儀數據，證實該物體包含一個黑洞<ref name="ESO2208"/><ref name="Shadow" />。這張影像經過五年的計算處理才得以完成<ref>{{Cite web |last=Hensley |first=Kerry |date=2022-05-12 |title=First Image of the Milky Way's Supermassive Black Hole |url=https://aasnova.org/2022/05/12/first-image-of-the-milky-ways-supermassive-black-hole/ |access-date=2022-05-13 |website=AAS Nova |language=en-US}}</ref>。這些數據由位於六個地理位置的八架電波望遠鏡觀測站收集，經由{{link-en|孔徑合成|Aperture synthesis}}數據獲得的電波影像，僅由來源穩定的夜間觀測數據生成。人馬座A*的無線電發射以分鐘為單位變化，使分析複雜化<ref>{{cite journal |author=The Event Horizon Telescope Collaboration | title = First Sagittarius A* Event Horizon Telescope Results. III. Imaging of the Galactic Center Supermassive Black Hole | journal = The Astrophysical Journal Letters | date = 1 May 2022 | volume = 930 | issue = 2 | page = L14 | issn = 2041-8205 | eissn = 2041-8213 | doi = 10.3847/2041-8213/ac6429}}</ref>。

他們的結果給出了電波源的總體[[角直徑|角大小]]為{{val|51.8|2.3|ul=μas}}<ref name="Shadow">{{cite journal |author=The Event Horizon Telescope Collaboration | title = First Sagittarius A* Event Horizon Telescope Results. I. The Shadow of the Supermassive Black Hole in the Center of the Milky Way | journal = The Astrophysical Journal Letters | date = 1 May 2022 | volume = 930 | issue = 2 | page = L12 | issn = 2041-8205 | eissn = 2041-8213 | doi = 10.3847/2041-8213/ac6674}}</ref>。在距離{{Convert|26,000|ly|pc|lk=on|abbr=off}}處，這相當於{{Convert|51.8|e6km|e6mi|abbr=none}}的直徑。相比之下，地球距離[[太陽|太陽]] {{Convert|150|e6km|AU e6mi|lk=on|abbr=none}}，[[水星|水星]]在[[拱點|近日點]]時距離太陽{{Convert|46|e6km|AU e6mi|abbr=unit}}。人馬座A*每年的[[自行|自行]]約為[[赤經|赤經]] −2.70[[角秒#毫角秒及微角秒|mas]]，[[赤緯|赤緯]] −5.6mas<ref>[[#Backer|Backer and Sramek 1999]], § 3</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/journal/2041-8205/page/Focus_on_EHT|title=Focus on the First Event Horizon Telescope Results – The Astrophysical Journal Letters – IOPscience|website=iopscience.iop.org|access-date=2019-04-10|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514171744/https://iopscience.iop.org/journal/2041-8205/page/Focus_on_EHT|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/04/10/science/black-hole-picture.html|title=Black Hole Picture Revealed for the First Time|last=Overbye|first=Dennis|date=2019-04-10|work=The New York Times|access-date=2019-04-10|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2019-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521020231/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/04/10/science/black-hole-picture.html|url-status=live}}</ref>。
該望遠鏡對這些黑洞的量測比以前更嚴格地檢驗了愛因斯坦的[[相對論|相對論]]，結果完全吻合<ref name="NYT-20220512">{{Cite news |last=Overbye |first=Dennis |date=2022-05-12 |title=The Milky Way's Black Hole Comes to Light |language=en-US |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2022/05/12/science/black-hole-photo.html |access-date=2022-05-12 |issn=0362-4331}}</ref>。

2019年，使用安裝在飛機的[[同溫層紅外線天文台|同溫層紅外線天文台]]上的高解析度機載寬頻相機+（High-resolution Airborne Wideband Camera-Plus，HAWC +）進行的測量<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.sofia.usra.edu/science/instruments/hawc#|title=HAWC+, the Far-Infrared Camera and Polarimeter for SOFIA|date=2018|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2021-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210803210336/https://www.sofia.usra.edu/science/instruments/hawc|url-status=live}}</ref>，發現磁場導致周圍的氣體和塵埃環，其溫度範圍為{{Convert|-280|to|17500|F|K C}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.space.com/milky-way-monster-black-hole-cool-disk.html|title=The Milky Way's Monster Black Hole Has a Cool Gas Halo — Literally|work=Space.com|date=5 June 2019|access-date=19 June 2019|archive-date=19 June 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190619004814/https://www.space.com/milky-way-monster-black-hole-cool-disk.html|url-status=live}}</ref>，流入圍繞人馬座A*的軌道，維持著黑洞的低輻射<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.space.com/milky-way-supermassive-black-hole-magnetic-field-quiet.html|title=Magnetic Fields May Muzzle Milky Way's Monster Black Hole|work=Space.com|date=14 June 2019|access-date=19 June 2019|archive-date=18 June 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190618050808/https://www.space.com/milky-way-supermassive-black-hole-magnetic-field-quiet.html|url-status=live}}</ref>。

因為光源和地球之間的塵埃和氣體[[消光|消光]]的影響高達25[[星等|星等]]<ref name="Osterbrock">[[#Osterbrock|Osterbrock and Ferland 2006]], p. 390</ref>，使得天文學家始終無法在[[可見光|可見光]]中觀察到人馬座A*。

==超大質量黑洞假說==
多個研究隊都嘗試利用[[甚长基线干涉测量|甚長基線干涉儀]]（VLBI）以[[無線電頻譜|無線電頻譜]]拍攝人馬座A*的成像。以現今最高解像的量度（即[[波長|波長]]1.3毫米），人馬座A*約有37微角秒的大小。<ref name="EHS" />按距離26000[[光年|光年]]來計算，人馬座A*的[[直徑|直徑]]為4400萬公里，近0.3[[天文單位|天文單位]]。[[地球|地球]]與[[太陽|太陽]]的距離（1[[天文單位|天文單位]]）約為1億5千萬公里；而[[水星|水星]]最接近太陽的距離則為4600萬公里。

若人馬座A*剛好坐落在[[黑洞|黑洞]]的中央，其大小會因[[引力透镜|重力透鏡效應]]而被放大。根據[[廣義相對論|廣義相對論]]，若以4百萬[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]的[[黑洞|黑洞]]來比較，人馬座A*的可觀測大小最少也是該黑洞[[史瓦西半徑|史瓦西半徑]]的5.2倍。但是4百萬太陽質量的黑洞約有52微角秒，以人馬座A*的37微角秒來看，其大小明顯大了很多，所以相信人馬座A*的放射源並非在洞的中心，而是在周邊接近[[事件視界|事件視界]]的光亮點，有可能是在[[吸積盤|吸積盤]]或由吸積盤噴出的[[相對論性噴流|相對論性噴流]]。<ref name="EHS">{{Cite journal |last=Doeleman |first=Sheperd S. |last2=Weintroub |first2=Jonathan |last3=Rogers |first3=Alan E. E. |last4=Plambeck |first4=Richard |last5=Freund |first5=Robert |last6=Tilanus |first6=Remo P. J. |last7=Friberg |first7=Per |last8=Ziurys |first8=Lucy M. |last9=Moran |first9=James M. |last10=Corey |first10=Brian |last11=Young |first11=Ken H. |date=2008-09 |title=Event-horizon-scale structure in the supermassive black hole candidate at the Galactic Centre |url=http://www.nature.com/articles/nature07245 |journal=Nature |language=en |volume=455 |issue=7209 |doi=10.1038/nature07245 |issn=0028-0836 |access-date=2022-05-15 |archive-date=2022-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220515083838/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature07245 }}</ref>

人馬座A*的[[質量|質量]]估計為431 ± 38萬<ref name="Gillessen"/>、或410 ± 60萬[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]。<ref name="Ghez2">{{cite journal en|coauthor=''et al.''|last=Ghez|first=A. M.|year=2008|title=Measuring Distance and Properties of the Milky Way's Central Supermassive Black Hole with Stellar Orbits|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=689|pages=1044-62|doi=10.1086/592738}}</ref>設這些質量被限制在4400萬公里[[直徑|直徑]]的球體內，其[[密度|密度]]將會比以往估計的高出10倍。儘管可能有其他理論能解釋這種質量及大小，但人馬座A*萎縮成一個[[超大質量黑洞|超大質量黑洞]]的時間應比[[銀河系|銀河系]]的壽命短。<ref name="EHS"/>

現時已有對黑洞本身的直接觀測，相關照片發布於2022年5月12日，但在此前，觀測紀錄就已顯示應有一個黑洞位於人馬座A*附近。目前所探測到的[[無線電波|無線電波]]及[[紅外線|紅外線]][[能量|能量]]等等，乃是從掉入黑洞時被加熱至幾百萬度的[[氣體|氣體]]及塵埃所發出。黑洞本身相信只會發出[[霍金輻射|霍金輻射]]。

==觀測歷史==
[[卡尔·央斯基|卡尔·央斯基]]（Karl Jansky）被認為是射電天文學之父，他於1933年4月發現射電信號來自射手座方向的某個位置，指向銀河系的中心<ref>{{cite web |url=https://armaghplanet.com/karl-jansky-the-father-of-radio-astronomy.html |title=Karl Jansky: The Father of Radio Astronomy |date=29 August 2012 |access-date=2019-01-27 |archive-date=2019-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190628163259/http://www.armaghplanet.com/karl-jansky-the-father-of-radio-astronomy.html |url-status=live }}</ref>。 無線電源後來被稱為[[人馬座A|人馬座A]]。他的觀察結果並沒有像我們現在所知的銀河中心那樣向南延伸<ref name="goss_history">{{cite journal |last1=Goss |first1=W. M. |last2=McGee |first2=R. X. |title=The Discovery of the Radio Source Sagittarius A (Sgr A) |journal=The Galactic Center, Astronomical Society of the Pacific Conference Series |date=1996 |volume=102 |pages=369 |bibcode=1996ASPC..102..369G |url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1996ASPC..102..369G/abstract |access-date=25 February 2021 |archive-date=3 March 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303171739/https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1996ASPC..102..369G/abstract |url-status=live }}</ref>。 Jack Piddington 和 Harry Minnett 在[[悉尼|悉尼]]Potts Hill水庫使用[[联邦科学与工业研究组织|CSIRO]]射電望遠鏡進行的觀測發現了一個離散且明亮的“人馬座-天蠍座”射電源<ref name="piddington">{{cite journal |last1=Piddington |first1=J. H. |last2=Minnett |first2=H. C. |title=Observations of Galactic Radiation at Frequencies of 1200 and 3000 Mc/s. |journal=Australian Journal of Scientific Research a Physical Sciences |date=1 December 1951 |volume=4 |issue=4 |pages=459 |doi=10.1071/CH9510459 |bibcode=1951AuSRA...4..459P |url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1951AuSRA...4..459P/abstract |access-date=25 February 2021 |archive-date=13 April 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413090955/https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1951AuSRA...4..459P/abstract |url-status=live }}</ref> ，在使用{{Convert|80|ft|m|abbr=off|adj=on}}的[[联邦科学与工业研究组织|CSIRO]]多佛高地的射電望遠鏡進一步觀察後,在給《[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]》的一封信中被確定為可能的銀河中心<ref name="galactic_centre_mcgee">{{cite journal |last1=McGee |first1=R. X. |last2=Bolton |first2=J. G. |title=Probable observation of the galactic nucleus at 400 Mc./s. |journal=Nature |date=1 May 1954 |volume=173 |issue=4412 |pages=985–987 |doi=10.1038/173985b0 |bibcode=1954Natur.173..985M |s2cid=4188235 |url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1954Natur.173..985M/abstract |access-date=25 February 2021 |issn=0028-0836 |archive-date=30 January 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220130113909/https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1954Natur.173..985M/abstract |url-status=live }}</ref>。

[[File:Cloudlets_swarm_around_our_local_supermassive_black_hole.tif|thumb]]對富含分子氫的氣體雲的觀測，人馬座A*周圍的區域被圈出<ref>{{cite web |title=Cloudlets swarm around our local supermassive black hole |url=https://www.eso.org/public/images/potw1843a/ |website=www.eso.org |access-date=22 October 2018 |archive-date=22 October 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181022093902/https://www.eso.org/public/images/potw1843a/ |url-status=live }}</ref>]]

後來的觀察表明，人馬座A實際上由幾個重疊的子成分組成； 1974年2月13日至15日，天文學家布魯斯·巴利克(Bruce Balick)和羅伯特·布朗(Robert Brown) 使用[[美国国家射电天文台|美国国家射电天文台]]的基線乾涉儀發現了一個明亮且非常緊湊的組件Sgr A*<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Balick |first1=B. |last2=Brown |first2=R. L.|title=Intense sub-arcsecond structure in the galactic center|journal=Astrophysical Journal|date=1 December 1974|volume=194|issue=1|pages=265–270|doi=10.1086/153242|bibcode=1974ApJ...194..265B}}</ref><ref>[[#Melia|Melia 2007]], p. 7</ref>。Sgr A* 這個名字是布朗在1982年的一篇論文中創造的，因為射電源是“激发的”，並且[[激发态|激发态]]原子被用星號来表示<ref>{{Cite journal|arxiv=astro-ph/0305074 |title=The Discovery of Sgr A* |journal=Astronomische Nachrichten |volume=324 |issue=1 |page=497 |date=2003-05-06 |last1=Goss |first1=W. M. |last2=Brown |first2=Robert L. |last3=Lo |first3=K. Y. |doi=10.1002/asna.200385047 |bibcode=2003ANS...324..497G }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Precessing jets in Sagittarius A – Gas dynamics in the central parsec of the galaxy|first=R. L. |last=Brown |journal=Astrophysical Journal, Part 1 |volume=262 |date=1982-11-01 |pages=110–119 |bibcode=1982ApJ...262..110B|doi=10.1086/160401 }}</ref>。

[[馬克斯·普朗克地外物理學研究所|馬克斯·普朗克地外物理學研究所]]（Max Planck Institute for Extraterrestrial Physics）由Rainer Schödel所帶領的國際研究隊觀測了接近人馬座A*的星體[[S2_(恆星)|S2]]達十年，於2002年10月16日公佈人馬座A*為一大質量致密體的證據。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Schödel |first=R. |last2=Ott |first2=T. |last3=Genzel |first3=R. |last4=Hofmann |first4=R. |last5=Lehnert |first5=M. |last6=Eckart |first6=A. |last7=Mouawad |first7=N. |last8=Alexander |first8=T. |last9=Reid |first9=M. J. |last10=Lenzen |first10=R. |last11=Hartung |first11=M. |date=2002-10 |title=A star in a 15.2-year orbit around the supermassive black hole at the centre of the Milky Way |url=http://www.nature.com/articles/nature01121 |journal=Nature |language=en |volume=419 |issue=6908 |doi=10.1038/nature01121 |issn=0028-0836 |access-date=2022-05-15 |archive-date=2022-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220401030128/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature01121 }}</ref>從S2的[[克卜勒軌道|克卜勒軌道]]計算，人馬座A*的質量為260 ± 20萬[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]，[[半徑|半徑]]為120[[天文單位|天文單位]]。<ref name="Ghez1">{{Cite journal |last=Ghez |first=A. M. |last2=Duchêne |first2=G. |last3=Matthews |first3=K. |last4=Hornstein |first4=S. D. |last5=Tanner |first5=A. |last6=Larkin |first6=J. |last7=Morris |first7=M. |last8=Becklin |first8=E. E. |last9=Salim |first9=S. |last10=Kremenek |first10=T. |last11=Thompson |first11=D. |date=2003-04-01 |title=The First Measurement of Spectral Lines in a Short-Period Star Bound to the Galaxy’s Central Black Hole: A Paradox of Youth |url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/374804 |journal=The Astrophysical Journal |volume=586 |issue=2 |doi=10.1086/374804 |access-date=2022-05-15 |archive-date=2022-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220515083832/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/374804 }}</ref>期後的觀測估計人馬座A*的質量應為410萬太陽質量，[[體積|體積]]半徑少於45天文單位。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.astro.ucla.edu/~ghezgroup/gc/ |title=UCLA Galactic Center Group |accessdate=2009-11-11 |archive-date=2017-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626010742/http://www.astro.ucla.edu/~ghezgroup/gc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

於2004年11月，天文學家發現可能是[[中介質量黑洞|中介質量黑洞]]的[[GCIRS_13E|GCIRS 13E]]，其軌道距人馬座A*約3[[光年|光年]]。GCIRS 13E的質量為1300太陽質量，屬於有7個[[恆星|恆星]]的星團。這次觀測支持了超大質量黑洞會吸收周邊較細小黑洞及星體來增長的說法。

經過觀測人馬座A*16年，相信其質量為431 ± 38萬太陽質量。<ref name="Gillessen">{{Cite journal |last=Gillessen |first=S. |last2=Eisenhauer |first2=F. |last3=Trippe |first3=S. |last4=Alexander |first4=T. |last5=Genzel |first5=R. |last6=Martins |first6=F. |last7=Ott |first7=T. |date=2009-02-20 |title=MONITORING STELLAR ORBITS AROUND THE MASSIVE BLACK HOLE IN THE GALACTIC CENTER |url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/0004-637X/692/2/1075 |journal=The Astrophysical Journal |volume=692 |issue=2 |doi=10.1088/0004-637X/692/2/1075 |issn=0004-637X |access-date=2022-05-15 |archive-date=2022-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220512144005/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/0004-637X/692/2/1075 }}</ref>研究人員[[赖因哈德·根策尔|赖因哈德·根策尔]]認為已有初步證據證明超大質量黑洞的存在。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Beyond Any Reasonable Doubt: A Supermassive Black Hole Lives in Centre of Our Galaxy|url=https://www.universetoday.com/22104/beyond-any-reasonable-doubt-a-supermassive-black-hole-lives-in-centre-of-our-galaxy/|access-date=2022-05-15|date=2008-12-10|last=O'Neill|first=Ian|work=Universe Today|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220515083832/https://www.universetoday.com/22104/beyond-any-reasonable-doubt-a-supermassive-black-hole-lives-in-centre-of-our-galaxy/}}</ref>

在2015年1月5日，NASA報告說觀測到人馬座A*的[[X射線|X射線]]閃焰破紀錄的比平常亮了400倍。天文學家宣稱，這種不尋常的事件可能是由於一顆[[小行星|小行星]]落入黑洞被扯碎，或者是因氣體流入人馬座A*引發[[磁力線|磁力線]]糾纏造成的<ref name="NASA-20150105">{{cite web |last=Chou |first=Felicia |last2=Anderson |first2=Janet |last3=Watzke |first3=Megan |title=Release 15-001 – NASA's Chandra Detects Record-Breaking Outburst from Milky Way's Black Hole |url=http://www.nasa.gov/press/2015/january/nasa-s-chandra-detects-record-breaking-outburst-from-milky-way-s-black-hole/ |date=5 January 2015 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |access-date=6 January 2015 |archive-date=2015-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106100532/http://www.nasa.gov/press/2015/january/nasa-s-chandra-detects-record-breaking-outburst-from-milky-way-s-black-hole/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年5月13日，天文學家使用[[凱克天文台|凱克天文台]]目睹了人馬座A *突然變亮，比平時亮75倍，這表明超大質量黑洞可能遇到了另一個天體<ref>{{cite news |title=Our Galaxy's Supermassive Black Hole Has Emitted a Mysteriously Bright Flare |url=https://www.sciencealert.com/our-galaxy-s-supermassive-black-hole-just-mysteriously-got-really-really-bright |date=12 August 2019 |work=Science Alert |access-date=12 August 2019 |archive-date=12 August 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812120201/https://www.sciencealert.com/our-galaxy-s-supermassive-black-hole-just-mysteriously-got-really-really-bright |url-status=live }}</ref>。

